<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-142] Watching the Client RPC Stream (Ch 31)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-142</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre 2.x manual, section:&lt;br/&gt;
31.2.2. Watching the Client RPC Stream&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The parameter &quot;offset&quot; doesn&apos;t have any description.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should have a description, ideally a quick summary.  It should also point to the section in the manual that deals with offsets (currently 31.2.3. Client Read-Write Offset Survey).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
